1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,524
Baby Duck Goes UP. A story for a little one.

2
00:00:05,600 --> 00:00:08,284
Baby Duck saw a big, tall hill.

3
00:00:08,366 --> 00:00:09,898
I can't go up that!

4
00:00:11,366 --> 00:00:13,594
But TayTay Duck knew something.

5
00:00:13,666 --> 00:00:14,862
Yes you can.

6
00:00:15,666 --> 00:00:17,894
One step. Then another.

7
00:00:18,166 --> 00:00:19,266
Then another.

8
00:00:21,166 --> 00:00:22,266
One step...

9
00:00:22,566 --> 00:00:23,666
Then another...

10
00:00:23,966 --> 00:00:25,042
Keep going...

11
00:00:25,366 --> 00:00:26,538
Almost there...

12
00:00:26,766 --> 00:00:27,578
I did it!

13
00:00:29,100 --> 00:00:30,056
Yay Duck!

14
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:32,212
You did it, Baby Duck!

15
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:35,908
And Baby Duck laughed all the way down!

16
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,036
The End.

